Recipe Manager:

Here User can have 3 roles--> Creator,Moderator,Admin

Creator : This user can add the recipes.

Moderator : This user can see all the recipes added by different users and are not published.User can publish the content.

admin : This user can Add New user, see all the recipes which are published and can display the latest 5 recipes in Main Page.

Ruby version : ruby 193
Rails 3.0.0
Also used Angularjs,jQuery .
